---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Travel Stories | Fabrizio Vinciguerra"
description: "Fine art travel photography collection exploring landscapes, cities and quiet journeys around the world."
---

<section class="collection-hero">
  <img src="/assets/images/travel.jpg" alt="Travel Stories">

  <div class="collection-hero-content">
    <p class="subtitle">Collection 04</p>
    <h1>Travel Stories</h1>
    <p>Fragments of distant places, quiet journeys and unexpected light.</p>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="fine-art-story">

  <div class="story-text">
    <p>
      Every journey begins long before the photograph.
    </p>
  </div>

  {% for photo in travel %}
    <figure class="story-image {{ photo.class }} reveal">
      <img 
  src="{{ photo.src }}" 
  alt="{{ photo.alt }}"
     loading="lazy"
   decoding="async"
  class="lightbox-image"
  data-full="{{ photo.src }}"
  data-title=""
    >
    </figure>
  {% endfor %}

</section>

<section class="fine-art-story">

<div class="story-text">
<p>

Every journey begins long before the photograph.

</p>
</div>

{% for photo in travel %}

<figure class="story-image {{ photo.class }} reveal">
<img src="{{ photo.src }}" alt="{{ photo.alt }}">
</figure>

{% endfor %}

</section>